.TH HOPCODERX-DIAGNOSTICS 1 "HopCoderX local"
.SH NAME
hopcoderx diagnostics \- Diagnostics & maintenance
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hopcoderx diagnostics
.RI < subcommand >
.RI [ arguments ]
