.TP
\fBstats\fR
Run \(aqhopcoderx diagnostics stats \-\-help\(aq for more information
.TP
\fBdb\fR
Run \(aqhopcoderx diagnostics db \-\-help\(aq for more information
.TP
\fBcompletion\fR
Run \(aqhopcoderx diagnostics completion \-\-help\(aq for more information
.TP
\fBconfig\fR
Run \(aqhopcoderx diagnostics config \-\-help\(aq for more information
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR hopcoderx (1)
